'''Bharat Parv''' is a five-day festival organised by [[Ministry of Tourism (India)]], [[Government of India]] to showcase the cuisine and culture of different states of [[India]].<ref>http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/Bharat-Parv-event-begins-on-Delhis-Red-Fort-lawns/articleshow/50733939.cms</ref><ref>http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/bharat-parv-event-begins-on-red-fort-lawns/articleshow/50734160.cms</ref> It was inaugurated on 26th January 2018 and will continue till 31st January 2018. 

